amp;url=https%3A%2F%2F electronics.woot.com%2Foffers%2Fthe-legend-of-zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-3%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A% 2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F2%2F24260573%2Fzelda-echoes-of-wisdom-nintendo-switch-physical-game-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Woot &lt;/a>; 10 月 4 日之前售价 51.99 美元（折扣 8 美元）（或直到售完为止，售完之前短暂补货）。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;aside id=&quot;ENec9V&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;《智慧的回声》最好的技巧是将塞尔达变成一个地下城主&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24258654/the-legend-of-zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-edit-dungeons-links-awakening&quot;} ]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;vEt5ra&quot;>;&lt;em>;智慧回响&lt;/em>;与典型的塞尔达传说游戏有很大不同，不仅仅是因为它最后以该系列命名的角色为中心。它借用了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/19/20871958/legend-of-zelda-links-awakening-review-nintendo-switch- 的赤壁微型风格艺术设计update-graphics&quot;>;&lt;em>;林克的觉醒&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;是 2019 年的重制版，但将其重新混合到一个新的开放世界中。塞尔达不再仅仅依靠剑，而是使用她新的魔法三杆来创建副本......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260573 /zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-nintendo-switch-physical-game-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260573/zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-nintendo-switch-physical-game-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260573/zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-nintendo-switch-physical-game-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-02T15:48:11-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-02T15:48:11-04:00</updated><title>美国银行发生故障，显示账户余额被清空</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;钱包的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9BheYpWLJ1ez7iCIuKghR083Z34=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73627482/STK417_MONEY_CVIRGINIA_A.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3My7wh&quot;>;首先，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24257477/spotify-outage-down -website-app&quot;>;Spotify&lt;/a>;，然后 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/30/24258362/verizon-mobile-services-down-sos-mode&quot;>;Verizon &lt;/a>;，然后是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/30/24258362/verizon-mobile-services-down-sos-mode&quot;>;PlayStation&lt;/a>;，现在本周显然轮到美国银行发生故障了。一些客户报告周三访问他们的银行账户时出现问题，余额显示为 0 美元或“----”，而不是应有的内容。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TuF9tO&quot;>;DownDetector 上的报告在美国东部时间下午 1 点前激增，帖子遍布 X 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/BankOfAmerica/comments/1fuldts/boa_app_and_website_down /&quot;>;Reddit &lt;/a>;来自人们的报告称，他们的帐户余额没有显示任何内容（有些人提到，他们所欠的金额似乎显示准确）。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;pOg2rd&quot;>;我们验证了该银行的应用程序正在向客户显示“帐户暂时不可用”和“某些帐户和/或余额暂时不可用”的通知，正如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/ 之前报道的那样2024/10/02/business/bank-of-america-outage/index.html&quot;>;CNN&lt;/a>;。有些人...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance -blank-zero&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance-blank-zero" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance-blank-zero</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-02T15:25:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-02T15:25:30-04:00</updated><title> PUBG 开发商在任天堂诉讼中将 Palworld 制作为手机版</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示来自 Palworld 的 Cattiva 的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6DAVkwrKCQgLBKvzeHdaHX35h3A=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73627452/Palworld_Paldeck_08.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图像：Pocketpair&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;VyL6fS&quot;>;&lt;em>;Palworld&lt;/em>; 开发者 Pocketpair 可能面临的问题任天堂提起诉讼，但这并没有阻止它开发该游戏的移动版本。周三，《PUBG：绝地求生》的发行商 Krafton — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.krafton.com/news/press/%ED%81%AC%EB%9E%98 %ED%94%84%ED%86%A4-%ED%8C%B0%EC%9B%94%EB%93%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EB%B0%94%EC%9D%BC -%EA%B2%8C%EC%9E%84-%EA%B8%80%EB%A1%9C%EB%B2%8C-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EC%84% A0%EC%8A%A4/&quot;>;宣布获得&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;Palworld&lt;/em>;的许可，并将针对移动游戏进行优化，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.polygon. com/news/459122/palworld-mobile-pubg-studios&quot;>;正如&lt;em>;Polygon&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;之前报道的那样。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LtpBQH&quot;>;根据翻译版本Krafton 表示，这篇文章的目的是“忠实地重新诠释”Palworld 的“主要有趣元素，以适应移动环境”。 Krafton 还在 2018 年创建了《PUBG》的移动版本，并且 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2018/3/16/17128526/pubg-mobile-hands-on- review-vs-xbox-fortnite&quot;>;正如 The Verge 当时指出的那样&lt;/a>;，结果比预期要好。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;J5VKdb&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Palworld 是一个命中，很容易明白为什么 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/22/24047087/palworld-early-access-steam-xbox-gamepass&quot;}]}&#39;>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;QyAz6Y&quot;>;被称为“带枪的&lt;em>;神奇宝贝&lt;/em>;”，&lt;em>;Palworld&lt;/em>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/1/22/24047087/palworld-early-access-steam-xbox-gamepass&quot;>;一月份在 PC 和 Xbox 上发布后立即风靡&lt;/a>;，销量数百万... .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260580/pubg-developer-palworld-mobile-nintendo-lawsuit&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260580/pubg-developer-palworld-mobile-nintendo-lawsuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260580/pubg-developer-palworld-mobile-nintendo-lawsuit</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>